room_title: Escape room "Haunted Manor" by Room With a Clue in Honolulu
room_address: 1130 N Nimitz Hwy, Suite B295, Honolulu, HI 96817
room_description: Imagine you’re trapped in an eerie haunted manor. An evil spirit is trying to possess you, as it has done to many other victims. According to legend, it takes over your body, slowing draining the life out of you before capturing your soul! Knowing the demon’s name gives you power over it and will be used as your key to freedom.
